proposal.description: Adds the `predict` method for trained CatBoost models (CatBoostClassifier, CatBoostRegressor) to track feature-to-prediction data flow.
proposal.rationale: The `predict` method is core to applying a trained machine learning model. Tracking this function call establishes a crucial link between input features, the model artifact, and the resulting predictions, which is vital for complete provenance tracing. This API is commonly used but missing from the current KB.
